responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "780F6250460F5DD8F3BEF89B4FF57E1A", "Yes. Reports have already begun to filter in. The Settler Militia has been a valuable asset. More valued than all the glint in the Riverlands. But the war is eternal here. Go and rest and regain your strength. We shall sound the horns and light the bonfire when we need the militia to march again.")
